[size=3][u]Installation

[/u]1. Download v.236 from here: http://enbdev.com/index_en.html

2. Take from the "Wrapper Version" the "d3d9.dll" file and drop it
into the main skyrim folder

3. Download my ENB

4. Unzip the folder

5. Drop the content of the folder into your main skyrim folder

6. Have fun D;



[size=4][u]Recommended [/u][/size]

these mods are used in the Screenshots:

Pure Water

Enhanched Lights and FX

Book of Silence

Alternative Rock Textures

Real ICE - All in one

Visible Windows

Etheral Clouds

Beautiful Whiterun
